WEBVTT

00:02:27.600 --> 00:02:31.480
(Applause)

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:33.600
Ever since,

00:02:34.320 --> 00:02:38.080
all development in Bhutan
is driven by GNH,

00:02:39.080 --> 00:02:42.976
a pioneering vision
that aims to improve the happiness

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:44.840
and well-being of our people.

00:02:46.760 --> 00:02:48.936
But that's easier said than done,

00:02:48.960 --> 00:02:52.880
especially when you are one
of the smallest economies in the world.

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:56.680
Our entire GDP is less
than two billion dollars.

00:02:57.920 --> 00:03:00.416
I know that some of you here
are worth more --